    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor signs of road wear, such as small stone chips, while the interior remains comfortable and fully functional. Mechanically, the car is solid, shifts smoothly, and has been serviced regularly to ensure continued reliability. It is a dependable vehicle that offers a great balance of quality and value for its next owner.",
