      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, a mechanical masterpiece featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This vehicle is equipped with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for superior torque vectoring. The chassis integrity is flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal valve timing. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. With zero rod-bearing issues and a perfectly dry undercarriage, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The exterior finish is original and mirror-like, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage.",
